'''sinus''' (''plural'' '''sinuses''')

#{{anatomy}} A pouch or cavity in any organ or tissue, especially the [[paranasal sinus]].
#{{pathology}} An abnormal cavity or passage such as a [[fistula]], caused by the destruction of tissue.

